174
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:30,280
She has glossy hair.

175
00:10:32,060 --> 00:10:34,120
Glossy hair.

176
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:36,139
Her eyes are big and round.

177
00:10:36,139 --> 00:10:38,600
