181
00:10:47,180 --> 00:10:48,719
Eats a lot?

182
00:10:48,719 --> 00:10:52,439
Oh, I see. She needs to be a foodie.

183
00:10:52,439 --> 00:10:54,520
 And she likes sports. 

184
00:10:55,740 --> 00:10:58,760
