222
00:13:03,020 --> 00:13:05,020
Jogging home?

223
00:13:05,020 --> 00:13:07,519
I love sports.

224
00:13:07,519 --> 00:13:10,079
I love sports so much

225
00:13:10,079 --> 00:13:13,060
